      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental hemolysis measurements must be replicated across at least three independent test runs per operating point to support statistical comparison.",
      "rationale": "Three independent experimental runs per operating point were completed for the three matched conditions. Sample preparation and storage protocols documented and consistent."
