      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in validation simulations must be demonstrably equivalent to those used in the COU prediction simulations, with any differences quantified.",
      "rationale": "Inlet boundary condition profiles and blood rheology parameters differ between validation and COU simulations; differences were noted but not formally quantified or propagated. Equivalency not established at required gradation."
