    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility for regulatory submission. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed and the hemolysis index predictions fall below the clinical threshold across all assessed operating points. The assurance level is declared Medium, reflecting the team's judgment that the overall evidence package is adequate despite minor gaps in individual factors.",
